list.item:
Establishes an Advisory Commission consisting of
representatives of France, Turkey, the United Kingdom and the United
States to advise and assist the Director of NERWA in the execution of the program;

item.p:
Requests the Secretary General to appoint the
Director of NERWA on the
nomination of the Advisory Commission;

list.item:
Directs
NERWA to consult with the PCC in the best interests of their
respective tasks;
